es and themes, your site will print an error message on the <a href=\"@status_report\">status report</a>, the <a href=\"@modules_page\">modules page</a>, and the <a href=\"@themes_page\">themes page</a>. You can choose to only see these error messages if a security update is available, or to be notified about any newer versions.','none');
